Dataset class class BrainDataset(Dataset): def __init__(self, df, data_dir, is_test=False, transform=None): self.df = df self.data_dir = data_dir self.transform = transform self.is_test = is_test def __len__(self): return len(self.df) def __getitem__(self, idx): patient_id = f"{self.df.iloc[idx]['BraTS21ID']:05d}" patient_path = os.path.join(self.data_dir, patient_id) modalities = ["FLAIR", "T1w", "T1wCE", "T2w"] slices = [] for mod in modalities: mod_path = os.path.join(patient_path, mod) files = sorted( [f for f in os.listdir(mod_path) if f.endswith(".dcm")], key=lambda x: int(x.split("-")[-1].split(".")[0]), ) mid_idx = len(files) // 2 dicom = pydicom.dcmread(os.path.join(mod_path, files[mid_idx])) img = dicom.pixel_array.astype(np.float32) img = (img - img.min()) / (img.max() - img.min() + 1e-6) img = (img * 255).astype(np.uint8) img_pil = Image.fromarray(img).resize((256, 256), Image.BILINEAR) slices.append(np.array(img_pil)) image = np.stack(slices, axis=-1) if self.transform: augmented = self.transform(image=image) image = augmented["image"] else: image = torch.tensor(image.transpose(2, 0, 1), dtype=torch.float32) return ( image if self.is_test else ( image, torch.tensor(self.df.iloc[idx]["MGMT_value"], dtype=torch.float32), ) ) # Enhanced transforms with additional augmentation train_transform = A.Compose( [ A.HorizontalFlip(p=0.5), A.VerticalFlip(p=0.5), A.Rotate(limit=30, p=0.5), A.RandomBrightnessContrast(p=0.2), A.Normalize(mean=[0.485] * 4, std=[0.229] * 4), ToTensorV2(), ] ) val_transform = A.Compose( [A.Normalize(mean=[0.485] * 4, std=[0.229] * 4), ToTensorV2()] ) # Enhanced model setup with EfficientNet-B3 device = torch.device("cuda" if torch.cuda.is_available() else "cpu") model = timm.create_model("efficientnet_b3", pretrained=True) original_conv = model.conv_stem new_conv = nn.Conv2d( 4, original_conv.out_channels, kernel_size=original_conv.kernel_size, stride=original_conv.stride, padding=original_conv.padding, bias=False, ) with torch.no_grad(): new_conv.weight[:, :3] = original_conv.weight.clone() new_conv.weight[:, 3] = original_conv.weight.mean(dim=1) model.conv_stem = new_conv model.classifier = nn.Linear(model.classifier.in_features, 1) model = model.to(device) # Data split train_df, val_df = train_test_split( train_labels, test_size=0.2, stratify=train_labels["MGMT_value"], random_state=42 ) train_dataset = BrainDataset(train_df, "input/train", transform=train_transform) val_dataset = BrainDataset(val_df, "input/train", transform=val_transform) train_loader = DataLoader( train_dataset, batch_size=16, shuffle=True, num_workers=4, pin_memory=True ) val_loader = DataLoader( val_dataset, batch_size=16, shuffle=False, num_workers=4, pin_memory=True ) # Training setup with adjusted learning rate criterion = nn.BCEWithLogitsLoss() optimizer = optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=1e-4) scheduler = optim.lr_scheduler.ReduceLROnPlateau( optimizer, "max", patience=2, factor=0.5 ) best_auc = 0 # Extended training loop for epoch in range(12): model.train() running_loss = 0.0 for images, labels in tqdm(train_loader, desc=f"Epoch {epoch+1}"): images, labels = images.to(device), labels.to(device) optimizer.zero_grad() outputs = model(images).squeeze() loss = criterion(outputs, labels) loss.backward() optimizer.step() running_loss += loss.item() * images.size(0) epoch_loss = running_loss / len(train_dataset) model.eval() val_preds, val_true = [], [] with torch.no_grad(): for images, labels in val_loader: outputs = model(images.to(device)).squeeze().sigmoid().cpu() val_preds.append(outputs.numpy()) val_true.append(labels.numpy()) val_auc = roc_auc_score(np.concatenate(val_true), np.concatenate(val_preds)) print(f"Epoch {epoch+1} | Loss: {epoch_loss:.4f} | Val AUC: {val_auc:.4f}") if val_auc > best_auc: best_auc = val_auc torch.save(model.state_dict(), "best_model.pth") scheduler.step(val_auc) # Generate submission test_dir = "input/test" test_ids = [d for d in os.listdir(test_dir) if os.path.isdir(os.path.join(test_dir, d))] test_df = pd.DataFrame({"BraTS21ID": [int(id) for id in test_ids]}) test_df = test_df.sort_values("BraTS21ID") test_dataset = BrainDataset( test_df, "input/test", is_test=True, transform=val_transform ) test_loader = DataLoader(test_dataset, batch_size=16, shuffle=False, num_workers=4) model.load_state_dict(torch.load("best_model.pth")) model.eval() preds = [] with torch.no_grad(): for images in test_loader: outputs = model(images.to(device)).squeeze().sigmoid().cpu() preds.extend(outputs.numpy()) submission = pd.DataFrame( {"BraTS21ID": test_df["BraTS21ID"].astype(str).str.zfill(5), "MGMT_value": preds} ) submission.to_csv("submission/submission.csv", index=False) print(f"Best Validation AUC: {best_auc:.4f}")
